# Ne_Yonezawa_Project

Exact replication and extensions of **Yonezawa et al. (2000, Evolution)** for stage‑structured effective population size (Ny, Ne) in *Fritillaria camtschatcensis*.  
We reproduce Table 4 exactly, and add generics for other species plus a sexual‑only mode.

> Paper (OA PDF): Yonezawa K. et al. (2000) *Evolution* 54:2007–2013.  
> Formulas and inputs are taken directly from the paper’s Tables 2 and 4 and equation set (1)–(11). [1](https://sistemaupr-my.sharepoint.com/personal/raymond_tremblay_upr_edu/Documents/Microsoft%20Copilot%20Chat%20Files/Evolution%20-%202007%20-%20Yonezawa%20-%20FORMULATION%20AND%20ESTIMATION%20OF%20THE%20EFFECTIVE%20SIZE%20OF%20STAGE%E2%80%90STRUCTURED%20POPULATIONS%20IN.pdf)

